Instructions for intalling AberMUD 4.100.0:

  1) Uncompress and untar the distribution file:

     zcat AberMUD.4.100.0.tar.Z | tar -xvf -

  2) Edit the list of privileged users:

     vi DATA/priv/prived

  3) Build the abermud executable and socket.

     make abermud socket

  4) Type 'socket' to start it running ...

Enjoy!

					- Mycroft
